{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/devops-docker-mysql","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":"Inkyung"}},"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/devops-docker-mysql"},"id":"5990e83f-e828-565d-9aa2-4a0a23d0c3d9","excerpt":"1. mysql 컨테이너 생성 및 실행  명령어를 통해 컨테이너의 생성과 실행을 동시에 진행한다. 옵션 -v ${로컬 호스트의 저장소 경로}:/var/lib/mysql \n데이터 볼륨 옵션으로, 로컬 호스트의 저장소 경로를 mysql…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"locked\">🔒</span> 작성중</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-mysql-컨테이너-생성-및-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-mysql-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"1 mysql 컨테이너 생성 및 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. mysql 컨테이너 생성 및 실행</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">docker run</code> 명령어를 통해 컨테이너의 생성과 실행을 동시에 진행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ docker run -d -p 3306:3306 --name ${컨테이너 이름} -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=${PASSWORD} -v ${로컬 호스트의저장소 경로}:/var/lib/mysql mysql</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"옵션\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%B5%EC%85%98\" aria-label=\"옵션 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>옵션</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>-v ${로컬 호스트의 저장소 경로}:/var/lib/mysql <br/>\n데이터 볼륨 옵션으로, 로컬 호스트의 저장소 경로를 mysql의 저장소 경로에 마운트 하도록 설정한다. <br/>\n이 옵션을 설정하지 않으면 데이터 디렉토리가 컨테이너 내부에 생성되어 컨테이너 삭제시 저장소도 함께 지워지게 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-컨테이너-접속\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\" aria-label=\"2 컨테이너 접속 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 컨테이너 접속</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ docker exec -it ${CONTAINER_NAME} bash</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>패스워드는 위 컨테이너 생성 및 실행 명령어에서 지정한 <code class=\"language-text\">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD</code>환경 변수 값을 입력한다</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-mysql-서버-접속\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-mysql-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\" aria-label=\"3 mysql 서버 접속 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. mysql 서버 접속</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ mysql -u root -p </code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"4-mysql-기본-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-mysql-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"4 mysql 기본 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. mysql 기본 설정</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">mysql&gt; create user &#39;${USER_NAME}&#39;@&#39;%&#39; identified by &#39;${USER_PASSWORD}&#39;; </code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relati